<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Password Reset Link Expired - EngineSearch</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;">
        <h1 style="color: #856404;">Password Reset Link Expired</h1>

        <p>Hi {{ .Identity.traits.first_name }},</p>

        <p>The password reset link you clicked has expired. Please request a new password reset from the EngineSearch login page.</p>

        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
            If you need assistance, please contact our support team.
        </p>

        <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; margin: 30px 0;">

        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 12px;">
            Best regards,<br>
            The EngineSearch Team
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
